text: Anacasta biplagiata is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Stephan von Breuning in 1940. It is known from Malaysia.BioLib.cz - Anacasta biplagiata. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1940
